      text: '🎉 Welcome to WeChat Link Agent v{{version}}!\n\n📱 What is WeChat Link Agent?\nIt\'s a universal Agent remote controller — turning your WeChat into a remote panel for AI Agents.\nWhether on mobile or desktop, just send a message in WeChat to remotely control various AI Agents (Claude Code, OpenCode, CodeBuddy, etc.).\n\n✨ Slogan: Connect everything, Agents at your fingertips\n\n📋 Available Commands:\n  `/wlh` - Show help\n  `/wla` - List all Agents\n  `/wlc` - Clear conversation history\n  `/wls` - Show current status\n  `/stop` - Stop current task\n  `/all <prompt>` - Query all Agents in parallel\n\n🤖 Agent Scheduling:\n  `/<command> <prompt>` - Switch to an Agent and send (e.g. `/claude write a function`)\n  `/<cmd1> prompt1 /<cmd2> prompt2` - Multi-Agent parallel, merge by default (e.g. `/claude review code /opencode optimize performance`)\n  `/s /<cmd1> prompt1 /<cmd2> prompt2` - Multi-Agent parallel, split mode (e.g. `/s /claude review code /opencode optimize performance`)\n  `/<cmd1>:1 prompt1 /<cmd2>:2 prompt2` - Serial execution, order by number (e.g. `/claude:1 write a function /opencode:2 optimize it`)\n\n💡 Send a message directly to chat with the current Agent — no command prefix needed.‍​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌‌​‌​‌​‌‌​​​‌​​​‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​​‌​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​‍‍​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​​‌​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​‍',
      guide: '🎉 Bind successful! 🎉\n\nSend `Hello, WeChat Link Agent` to "WeChat Link Agent" in WeChat, and you will receive the welcome message.\n\n📱 You are seeing this prompt on your desktop. Please send a message from your phone WeChat.‍​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌‌​‌​‌​‌‌​​​‌​​​‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​​‌​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​‍‍​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​​‌​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌‌‌​​​​​‌​‌‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌‌​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌​​​‌‌​‌​​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​‌​‌‌​‌​‌‌​​​​‌​‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌‌​​‌​‌​‌‌​‌‌‌​​‌‌‌​‌​​‍',
